􏱭1􏱮􏱕􏱖􏱫Going Forward􏱬
􏱩The creation of sign realities must be codified􏱪􏱟􏱠􏱧􏱨
􏱩We need semantics that properly allow realties to be created with signs injected into them􏱪􏱟􏱠􏱧􏱨
􏱩This language must explain why signs are visible to the reality caller, and how the caller remains invisible to the callees􏱪􏱟􏱠􏱧􏱨
􏱩The rephrasing of these questions are as followed􏱪􏱟􏱠􏱧􏱨
􏱩how do we enter different realities as simulacrums?􏱪􏱟􏱠􏱧􏱨
􏱩How are our simulacrums kept unaware of us?􏱪􏱟􏱠􏱧􏱨